class.name: StoreSubscriptionInfoRenewalInfo
class.brief_description: Contains verified renewal metadata for a subscription.
class.description: This class wraps StoreKit renewal information and is only created from verified renewal data.

members.member: The app account token used when purchasing, as a UUID string. Returns an empty string when not set.
The app transaction identifier associated with the subscription. Returns an empty string when unavailable.
The current product identifier for the subscription group.
The original transaction identifier for the subscription. Returns [code]0[/code] when unavailable.
